{"tid":1145042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[皇室添丁]  梅根BB今亮相 邀美電視台老友採訪惹不滿","createTime":"2019-05-08T12:16:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T07:17:09.000Z","uid":241093,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c33240a539614950107b9395c7c35d11880d5679","tid":1145042,"uid":241093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:16:56.000Z","msg":"英國哈里王子與夫人梅根將安排寶寶周三在溫莎堡亮相，但對採訪的安排卻惹起不滿。<br />\n<br />\n哈里與梅根為保私人空間，生產過程相當秘密，產後出院不抱嬰見傳媒。哈里曾表示，兒子亮相時，會邀請英國新聞聯合社（Press Association）派一小隊人拍攝和採訪，僅一名影片攝影師、一名照片攝影師以及一名記者，之後負責發放採訪內容及照片給全球的傳媒機構。不過，兩人同時堅持邀請美國哥倫比亞廣播公司（CBS）派攝影隊採訪，更指定該台晨早節目主持人金格（Gayle King）參與。金格是梅根的好友，梅根2月在紐約開產前派對，金格也是來賓。<br />\n<br />\n英國傳媒引述消息人士報道，有關安排令白金漢宮和英國傳媒震驚。消息人士解釋，有關安排是要「反映國際對這件事情的關注」，但英國傳媒憤怒，皇室也感到擔心，報道形容這個安排猶如向英聯邦國家的傳媒「摑了一巴掌」。英女皇名義上是澳洲、加拿大、新西蘭等英聯邦國家的國家元首。<br />\n<br />\n哈里的兒子出生的消息公佈後，周一和周二都有民眾在溫莎堡外聚集送上祝福，有民眾表示︰<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「我想看看寶寶的長相，因為梅根的混血兒，我很好奇呢。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》/法新社<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190508&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59575850\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190508%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59575850&d=fyMqA0bs77BZF9qEbHCyfseYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=5edc91d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190508%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59575850&h=4d517628\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190508&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59575850</a>"},{"pid":"904bd97cab7679786a2ad46038079bd24e9b9d49","tid":1145042,"uid":249885,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:39:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">NIGGERS CANT BE ROYAL</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"0b7cf719c612370158d1da51aa93ebf2ea57f300","tid":1145042,"uid":96743,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:40:21.000Z","msg":"鬼叫你當年殺人老母<br />\n而家個孫就係想激死你"},{"pid":"1a199482fc42ff4db4e4d7781b5f5d046ebe9b67","tid":1145042,"uid":241093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T14:21:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e99a798a4e6e8121b491bddc3d758f59ef4f1913","tid":1145042,"uid":49549,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T14:22:58.000Z","msg":"唔係話歧視黑人<br />\n但佢真係幾令人反感"},{"pid":"5d8fe1b5c3d1591fde56c254cbe655a0acf3285e","tid":1145042,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T14:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />d負面新聞 係咪想追上侵?"},{"pid":"ccb260f65e0477ef5975c2d755dfc77c02a1dcc7","tid":1145042,"uid":187961,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T14:38:50.000Z","msg":"佢就係典型想做皇室成員享受榮華富貴，但從來無視背後的責任和傳統的人，只係想攞雀數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e46759a49e1496005e244baa86ffe2080aa1424d","tid":1145042,"uid":75610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T14:49:35.000Z","msg":"大巴打落事頭婆塊面度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"657b92ca6745454118834c3d0b1b26cd3662e778","tid":1145042,"uid":167032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T14:54:36.000Z","msg":"英國而家都親美咪有佢囉"},{"pid":"043dce303895627e48276b27b2ba7c5efc08315a","tid":1145042,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T14:58:03.000Z","msg":"黑人皇子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710a94c607f325ee8fd25e8ee25044f1d9a0bd31","tid":1145042,"uid":30253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T07:17:09.00